<title type="html"><![CDATA[4/20(Thu.)12 Taiwan night markets to satisfy street food cravings./5 ways to help yourself get over ... (Host William)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=719&amp;p=747#p747"><![CDATA[
We will hold an on-site meeting only.<br />摩斯漢堡明曜店(每人低消 :60元)<br />台北市仁愛路4段151巷37號地下室.<br />MRT忠孝敦化站3號出口 , 明曜百貨後方第二個巷子口<br /><br />Royal 台北 ( Thursday )<br /><br />**** NEW*** Meeting time agenda:7:00-9:00 PM<br />7:00-7:30 Chatting time with your favorite drink, and introduction of the meeting by the host<br />7:30-8:00 Discussion of the first topic<br />8:00-8:05 Take a group photo<br />8:05-8:30 Discussion of the second topic<br />8:30-9:00 Individual Presentation (we will be divided into two groups,<br />each person will have two minutes to give a presentation on any topic of that day.)<br /><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Sect.1<br />12 Taiwan night markets to satisfy street food cravings.<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://hoponworld.com/taiwan-night-markets/">https://hoponworld.com/taiwan-night-markets/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions, <br />1. Have you ever been to the night markets in Taiwan, specifically the ones in the 12 districts？<br />2. Have you ever accompanied foreign friends to a night market? How would you introduce a night market to them? <br />3. Where are the best night market in Taiwan?<br />4. Which night market foods do you like the best?<br />5. Why you absolutely must visit a night market in Taiwan ?<br /><br />Sect.2<br />5 ways to help yourself get over a big mistake. <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.inc.com/minda-zetlin/5-ways-to-help-yourself-get-over-a-big-mistake.html">https://www.inc.com/minda-zetlin/5-ways ... stake.html</a><!-- m --><br />1. Do you ask for help from your family or friends when you make a mistake? <br />2. What to do when you've made a big mistake?<br />3. What is the worst mistake you have ever done?<br />4. Is it bad to make a mistake?<br />5. What do you think might help you not make this mistake again?<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Fri Apr 14, 2023 11:47 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
